s($,"aRt","arR",()=>{var q=t.N
return A.av(["change_language","Change Language","hero_title","DISCOVER YOUR BEST SELF","hero_description","With Apparelte, discover outfit suggestions shared by thousands of users. Access details and purchase links for each piece in outfits you see in your feed with a single tap. No more wondering where to find a clothing item you love.","watch_intro","Watch Intro","download_on","Download on the","app_store","App Store","get_it_on","GET IT ON","google_play","Google Play","features_grid_title","TAKE YOUR PLACE IN FASHION WITH APPARELTE","features_grid_subtitle","Elevate your fashion experience with the most loved features in the app","feature_discover_title","Discover Outfits","feature_discover_desc","Get inspired by discovering outfits shared by thousands of users. Quickly find outfits that suit you perfectly by filtering by categories.","feature_link_title","Need a Link?","feature_link_desc","Instantly see store links for each piece in an outfit you like. Access brand, price, and size information, and learn immediately where to source products.","feature_profile_title","Create a Profile","feature_profile_desc","Create your own profile, share your outfits, and become part of the fashion community. Gain followers, collect likes, and become a style icon.","feature_link_tablet_title","Can I Get the Link?","features_section_title","EXPLORE OUTFITS THAT CATCH YOUR INTEREST","features_section_subtitle","Discover outfits you like and purchase each piece immediately. Apparelte makes it easier to navigate the fashion world and become stylish.","feature_details_title","Access outfit details instantly","feature_details_desc","See brand, model, and price information for all pieces in each outfit and access purchase links with a single touch. Creating your favorite style has never been this easy.","feature_categories_title","Discover outfits by category","feature_categories_desc","Browse hundreds of specially selected outfits in categories including sports, casual, office, evening, and many more. Make your style suitable for any environment with outfits specific to the categories you're interested in.","feature_rate_title","Rate and comment on outfits","feature_rate_desc","Vote, rate, and comment on outfits you like. Discover and get inspired by the most popular outfits in the community.","feature_alternatives_title","Discover similar products and alternatives","feature_alternatives_desc","See similar alternatives to a piece you like in different price ranges. Make choices that best suit your budget and style.","focus_section_title","BECOME A FASHION GURU","focus_section_subtitle","Reflect your style with your personal profile. View the outfits you've shared, interact with your followers, and take your place in the fashion community.","focus_collection_title","Manage Your Personal Collection","focus_collection_desc","View all the outfits you've shared and saved in your profile. Track your most liked outfits and continually update your collection.","focus_followers_title","Expand Your Follower Network","focus_followers_desc","Interact with followers who like your style, follow users with similar styles. Get inspired and inspire others in your fashion community.","focus_profile_title","Customize Your Profile","focus_profile_desc","Edit your profile photo, biography, and personal interests. Create a unique profile that reflects your style and fashion taste.","tools_section_title","STYLES THAT CAPTURE YOUR MOOD","tools_section_subtitle","Apparelte features category-based outfits specially prepared for every style and every environment. Use categories to reach the outfit you're looking for faster and show your style in every setting.","tools_casual_title","Daily & Casual Outfits","tools_casual_desc","Stylish and comfortable outfits you can use comfortably in your daily life. Ideal choices for school, meeting friends, or weekend outings.","tools_office_title","Office & Work Outfits","tools_office_desc","Elegant and impressive work outfits that will complete your professional look. Choices you can wear confidently in meetings and work environments.","tools_party_title","Evening & Party Outfits","tools_party_desc","Eye-catching and striking outfits for special invitations, parties, and evening events. Special choices that will make you stand out with your style.","tools_sport_title","Sports & Active Life","tools_sport_desc","Outfits that allow you to look both comfortable and stylish while doing sports. Choices that will increase your motivation at the gym, on the running track, or during outdoor activities.","tools_more_title","AND MORE...","tools_more_desc","Discover thousands of outfits in many categories including seasonal collections, special day outfits, holiday styles, and more. Access unlimited style opportunities with Apparelte.","team_section_title","Apparelte Team","team_role_senior_flutter","Senior Flutter Developer","team_role_flutter","Flutter Developer","team_role_ui_backend","UI/UX Designer & Backend Developer","footer_copyright","\xa9 VyrinLabs. All rights reserved."],q,q)})
s($,"aRv","aB8",()=>{var q=t.N
return A.av(["change_language","Vaheta Keelt","hero_title","AVASTA OMA PARIM MINA","hero_description","Apparelte abil avasta tuhandete kasutajate jagatud r\xf5ivakomplekte. P\xe4\xe4se ligi igale riideesemele ja ostulingile \xfchekordse puudutusega. Enam pole vaja muretseda, kust leida armastatud r\xf5ivat\xfckke.","watch_intro","Vaata Tutvustust","download_on","Lae alla","app_store","App Store","get_it_on","SAADAVAL","google_play","Google Play","features_grid_title","V\xd5TA OMA KOHT MOEMAAILMAS APPARELTE ABIL","features_grid_subtitle","T\xf5sta oma moodekogemus k\xf5rgemale tasemele rakenduse k\xf5ige armastatud funktsioonidega","feature_discover_title","Avasta Komplekte","feature_discover_desc","Saa inspiratsiooni, avastades tuhandete kasutajate jagatud r\xf5ivakomplekte. Leia kiiresti endale sobivaid komplekte kategooriate j\xe4rgi filtreerides.","feature_link_title","Vaja Linki?","feature_link_desc","N\xe4e koheselt poelinke iga meeldiva komplekti elemendi kohta. P\xe4\xe4se ligi br\xe4ndi, hinna ja suuruse teabele ning saa kohe teada, kust tooteid soetada.","feature_profile_title","Loo Profiil","feature_profile_desc","Loo oma profiil, jaga oma komplekte ja saa moe kogukonna osaks. Kogu j\xe4lgijaid, saa meeldimisi ja muutu stiiliikoniks.","feature_link_tablet_title","Kas Saan Linki?","features_section_title","UURI KOMPLEKTE, MIS K\xd6IDAVAD T\xc4HELEPANU","features_section_subtitle","Avasta meeldivaid komplekte ja osta iga osa kohe. Apparelte muudab moemaailmas navigeerimise ja stiilseks saamise lihtsamaks.","feature_details_title","P\xe4\xe4se komplekti detailidele ligi kohe","feature_details_desc","N\xe4e iga komplekti k\xf5igi osade br\xe4ndi, mudelit ja hinnateavet ning p\xe4\xe4se ligi ostulingidele \xfche puudutusega. Oma lemmikstiiili loomine pole kunagi olnud nii lihtne.","feature_categories_title","Avasta komplekte kategooriate kaupa","feature_categories_desc","Sirvi sadu spetsiaalselt valitud komplekte kategooriates, sealhulgas sport, argip\xe4ev, kontor, \xf5htu ja palju muud. Muuda oma stiil keskkonnale sobivaks, kasutades huvipakkuvate kategooriate spetsiifilisi komplekte.","feature_rate_title","Hinda ja kommenteeri komplekte","feature_rate_desc","H\xe4\xe4leta, hinda ja kommenteeri meeldivaid komplekte. Avasta ja saa inspiratsiooni kogukonna k\xf5ige populaarsematest komplektidest.","feature_alternatives_title","Avasta sarnaseid tooteid ja alternatiive","feature_alternatives_desc","Vaata meeldiva riideeseme sarnaseid alternatiive erinevates hinnavahemikes. Tee valikuid, mis sobivad k\xf5ige paremini sinu eelarve ja stiiliga.","focus_section_title","SAA MOEGUROONIKS","focus_section_subtitle","Peegelda oma stiili isikliku profiiliga. Vaata jagatud komplekte, suhtle j\xe4lgijatega ja v\xf5ta oma koht moemaailmas.","focus_collection_title","Halda Isiklikku Kollektsiooni","focus_collection_desc","Vaata k\xf5iki komplekte, mida oled jaganud ja salvestanud oma profiilis. J\xe4lgi enim meeldinud komplekte ja uuenda pidevalt oma kollektsiooni.","focus_followers_title","Laienda J\xe4lgijate V\xf5rgustikku","focus_followers_desc","Suhtle j\xe4lgijatega, kellele meeldib sinu stiil, j\xe4lgi sarnase stiiliga kasutajaid. Saa inspiratsiooni ja inspireeri teisi oma moemaailmas.","focus_profile_title","Kohanda Oma Profiili","focus_profile_desc","Muuda oma profiilipilti, elulugu ja isiklikke huve. Loo ainulaadne profiil, mis peegeldab sinu stiili ja moemaitset.","tools_section_title","STIILID, MIS TABAVAD TUJU","tools_section_subtitle","Apparelte pakub kategooriatel p\xf5hinevaid komplekte, mis on spetsiaalselt ette valmistatud igale stiilile ja keskkonnale. Kasuta kategooriaid, et j\xf5uda otsitava komplektini kiiremini ja n\xe4idata oma stiili igas keskkonnas.","tools_casual_title","Igap\xe4evased ja Casual Komplektid","tools_casual_desc","Stiilsed ja mugavad komplektid, mida saad kasutada igap\xe4evaelus. Ideaalsed valikud kooliks, s\xf5pradega kohtumiseks v\xf5i n\xe4dalavahetuse v\xe4ljas\xf5itudeks.","tools_office_title","Kontori ja T\xf6\xf6 Komplektid","tools_office_desc","Elegantsed ja muljetavaldavad t\xf6\xf6komplektid, mis t\xe4iendavad professionaalset v\xe4limust. Valikud, mida saad kindlalt kanda koosolekutel ja t\xf6\xf6keskkonnas.","tools_party_title","\xd5htu ja Peo Komplektid","tools_party_desc","Pilkup\xfc\xfcdvad ja silmatorkavad komplektid erilisteks kutseteks, pidudeks ja \xf5htu\xfcritusteks. Erilised valikud, mis panevad sind stiiliga silma paistma.","tools_sport_title","Sport ja Aktiivne Elu","tools_sport_desc","Komplektid, mis v\xf5imaldavad spordi tegemisel n\xe4ha v\xe4lja nii mugav kui stiilne. Valikud, mis suurendavad motivatsiooni j\xf5usaalis, jooksurajal v\xf5i v\xe4litegevustes.","tools_more_title","JA PALJU MUUD...","tools_more_desc","Avasta tuhandeid komplekte paljudes kategooriates, sealhulgas hooajalised kollektsioonid, erip\xe4eva komplektid, puhkusestiilid ja palju muud. P\xe4\xe4se ligi piiramatutele stiilimaailmale Apparelte abil.","team_section_title","Apparelte Meeskond","team_role_senior_flutter","Vanem Flutter Arendaja","team_role_flutter","Flutter Arendaja","team_role_ui_backend","UI/UX Disainer ja Backend Arendaja","footer_copyright","\xa9 VyrinLabs. K\xf5ik \xf5igused kaitstud."],q,q)})
